WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  'Bipaire' is a 'Workbench' game like 'Shangai', 'Dragon' or any
other similar games where you try to find pairs of matching tiles,
but unlike the oriental games, any visible tile can be choosen and
matched with another similar tile.

  When you find a pair of similar tiles, this pair is removed from
the board, this may reveal part of a tile located under. Continue
to find all the remaining pairs until there are no tiles left or
there are no pairs of similar tiles.

  When you complete a board, the game displays a new board and the
game continues. Can you complete all boards included in the game?

  Have fun!

